{"_path":"/construction/c02","_dir":"construction","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"郵政物流中心","description":null,"image":"/images/construction/c02-1.jpeg","sequence":2,"category":"工商發展","status":"1.完工","type":"grey","budget":"220億","link":"https://www.post.gov.tw/post/internet/Group/index.jsp?ID=1570265448379","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2022-07-05T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"郵政物流中心"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"郵政物流中心"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"計畫概要"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"計畫概要"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"項目 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://www.post.gov.tw/post/internet/Group/index.jsp?ID=1570265448379"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":" 郵政物流中心"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"類別 工商發展 - CON-02"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"開工日期 2018-08-05"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"完工日期 2022-07-05"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"經費 220 億"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"狀態 完成"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2022/7/5 日申報竣工，7 月 12 日至 7 月 15 日辦理初驗，8 月 2 日取得使用執照。2023 年 2 月已經啟動營運。PChome 進駐 租用 15 年。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"建設詳情-郵政物流園區"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建設詳情-郵政物流園區"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中華郵政斥資 220 億元打造「郵政物流園區」，佔地 17.14 公頃，涵蓋郵政物流中心、北台灣郵件作業中心、郵政資訊中心、郵政訓練中心及工商服務中心等 5 棟建築物，2023 年 1 月起分階段啟動營運，將有一部分人員先進駐，未來台北、桃園的郵件中心都將進行整併，移至 A7，預計未來至少可創造 6,000 個工作機會。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中華郵政以建置智慧園區為目標，導入多項自動化設備進行郵件處理作業，推動物流共享平台，以及跨境電+I5 子商務物流服務，吸引很多廠商關注，還可望成為東亞地區跨境物流示範基地。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"園區仿效美國蘋果電腦在加州庫帕提諾新總部 Apple Park「與自然共存」生態圈工法，建置寬 40 米、縱深 400 米，面積逾 4000 坪的郵政形象公園，連結近 2 公頃滯洪池，形成自然生態景觀，提供員工及附近居民的休憩場所。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"郵政物流中心地上八層、地下一層，主要樓層四層，每層四倉儲單元，共有 16 倉儲單元，倉儲面積約 4.8 萬坪，總樓地板面積達 6 萬 9,686 坪，設置兩座立體迴旋車道及 218 個裝（卸）貨月台。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"c02-01.jpeg","src":"/images/construction/c02-1.jpeg"},"children":[]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"郵政物流中心","depth":2,"text":"郵政物流中心","children":[{"id":"計畫概要","depth":3,"text":"計畫概要"},{"id":"建設詳情-郵政物流園區","depth":3,"text":"建設詳情-郵政物流園區"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:construction:c02.md","_source":"content","_file":"construction/c02.md","_extension":"md"}